replies.body:
Please do allow us to switch the champion/announcer languages at-will.

Some of us want to hear a certain maniacal laugh {{champion:222}}... VoHiYo
...or a certain questionable death vocalization {{champion:103}} 

Jokes aside. If you're going to shut the door on custom skins, at least provide us with access to the official audio of non-local regions.

{{sticker:sg-soraka}}
